Species metadata description

Biodiversity mapping

The following pdf gives a description of the data used in the pipeline run that corresponds to the folder this document resides in. It should be used as a guide for anyone who wants to know more about the data used in the corresponding outputs (maps and datasets) and/or would like to replicate the data.

We begin with basic information about the pipeline run.
